127
00:10:29,380 --> 00:10:32,580
(Tales of Herding Gods Season 3)

128
00:10:34,530 --> 00:10:36,980
So his so-called Domineering Body

129
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:39,130
is actually nothing extraordinary.

130
00:10:39,530 --> 00:10:41,730
But he believes in it with unshakable confidence

131
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:45,630
and has beaten so many talents and geniuses,
making them flee in disgrace.

132
00:10:46,660 --> 00:10:50,250
What about the Domineering Body Triple-Elixir Skill
he practices? There must be something unique about it.

133
00:10:51,260 --> 00:10:52,870
The Triple-Elixir Skill

134
00:10:53,330 --> 00:10:58,320
is simply the most basic Guiding Skill
to keep healthy in the old era.

135
00:11:03,460 --> 00:11:05,960
If only ordinary people before the disaster

136
00:11:06,030 --> 00:11:07,900
could practice this technique,

137
00:11:08,830 --> 00:11:11,010
then how did the Sect Master awaken his Mortal Body?

138
00:11:11,860 --> 00:11:13,650
Was he born before the disaster?

139
00:11:14,730 --> 00:11:16,360
Where was Mu really born?

140
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:20,130
Carefree Township.

141
00:11:21,160 --> 00:11:23,270
Where is this Carefree Township?

142
00:11:26,060 --> 00:11:27,980
If you are interested, my friend,

143
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,360
we can

144
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,490
leave the village tonight

145
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:34,760
and search for it in the darkness
at the source of the Yong River.

146
00:11:39,460 --> 00:11:41,390
Do not damage the sacred tree!

147
00:11:46,660 --> 00:11:50,660
He's developed his own Great Unity Technique!

148
00:11:54,700 --> 00:11:56,290
When did you all arrive?

149
00:11:57,230 --> 00:12:00,050
"To follow one's true will
and live in full accord with nature

150
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:01,520
is the Way."

151
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:05,780
Sect Master, the way you immerse yourself in the Way
is truly remarkable.

152
00:12:06,560 --> 00:12:07,590
King Lu, you flatter me.

153
00:12:09,730 --> 00:12:11,360
Mr. Qin, you must be hungry.

154
00:12:12,410 --> 00:12:12,940
Here.

155
00:12:16,700 --> 00:12:19,130
These pheasants were raised by the former Saintess.

156
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:20,890
Grandma Si raised them?

157
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:24,160
Too bad someone ate half of the Nine-Leaf Lingzhi

158
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:25,930
in the Medicine King Hall.

159
00:12:26,130 --> 00:12:28,760
Otherwise, we could use it to nourish you.

160
00:12:31,700 --> 00:12:32,890
I just remembered.

161
00:12:32,930 --> 00:12:34,990
As an Erudite of the Academy,
I've barely attended any classes there.

162
00:12:35,730 --> 00:12:36,960
I plan to leave today.

163
00:12:41,300 --> 00:12:44,390
In every sense, we should ask you to stay longer,

164
00:12:44,700 --> 00:12:46,260
but your studies come first.

165
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:48,430
We won't keep you.

166
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:51,760
Your studies come first.

167
00:12:52,260 --> 00:12:54,190
Do come back often...

168
00:12:55,460 --> 00:12:56,990
I will.

169
00:13:18,670 --> 00:13:21,720
This new Sect Master is really something.

170
00:13:22,100 --> 00:13:24,060
The teleportation art relies on numerology,

171
00:13:24,060 --> 00:13:26,180
and the Great Unity Technique depends on comprehension.

172
00:13:26,460 --> 00:13:29,000
Yet he mastered both in just over ten days.

173
00:13:29,530 --> 00:13:33,200
Such talent and insight are rarely seen in the world.

174
00:13:33,330 --> 00:13:35,260
True.

175
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:38,140
But he still can't match the Imperial Preceptor,

176
00:13:38,140 --> 00:13:40,870
a sage seen once in five centuries.

177
00:13:41,130 --> 00:13:41,960
That's not necessarily true.

178
00:13:42,700 --> 00:13:44,450
We only know what we've witnessed.

179
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:46,740
He may have grasped even more.

180
00:13:48,900 --> 00:13:51,730
I can't wait to see him

181
00:13:51,830 --> 00:13:55,060
lead our sect to new glory.

182
00:13:58,700 --> 00:14:01,580
Our holy land is now above Guazhou?

183
00:14:01,830 --> 00:14:06,110
Lately, the imperial relatives of Yankang
have rebelled there.

184
00:14:07,300 --> 00:14:08,400
Sect Master!

185
00:15:16,530 --> 00:15:17,190
My lord,

186
00:15:17,460 --> 00:15:19,300
a kid popped out of nowhere.

187
00:15:19,900 --> 00:15:20,960
No need to be alarmed.

188
00:15:21,530 --> 00:15:23,000
I just want a ride to the capital.

189
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:25,460
From Guazhou to the capital?

190
00:15:25,660 --> 00:15:26,890
That'll be 100 Dafeng coins.

191
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:28,420
That much?

192
00:15:29,500 --> 00:15:31,560
Where else will you find such a fair price?

193
00:15:32,900 --> 00:15:36,430
Times are hard. There's war every day. Danger is everywhere.

194
00:15:37,660 --> 00:15:40,480
We risk our lives with every trip,

195
00:15:41,400 --> 00:15:43,490
so of course we charge more.

196
00:15:47,660 --> 00:15:49,560
These people don't look like proper boatmen.

197
00:15:49,630 --> 00:15:50,860
They're clearly bandits!

198
00:15:57,330 --> 00:15:58,610
Please, sir, take the honored seat!

199
00:16:01,830 --> 00:16:02,700
Do you feel good?

200
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,090
Sir,

201
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:13,170
after my father visited the Imperial Preceptor that night,

202
00:16:13,400 --> 00:16:14,490
the Three-Marvel Fort in Guazhou,

203
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:15,660
the Liqing Palace in Linzhou,

204
00:16:15,700 --> 00:16:17,460
and the Beggar Sect in Pingzhou all rebelled.

205
00:16:17,830 --> 00:16:19,790
I heard Emperor Yanfeng was so enraged

206
00:16:19,900 --> 00:16:23,130
that he sent Consort Che, who came
from the Three-Marvel Fort, into a cold palace.

207
00:16:23,860 --> 00:16:27,050
Send my words to all the sects.
Gather forces on the Southern Border.

208
00:16:37,460 --> 00:16:39,190
The Imperial Preceptor has let this rebellion drag on.

209
00:16:39,760 --> 00:16:41,290
When will he act?

210
00:16:57,900 --> 00:16:59,490
It's the insect army of the Three-Marvel Fort!

211
00:17:01,090 --> 00:17:02,060
Change course!

212
00:17:02,430 --> 00:17:03,330
Increase firepower!

213
00:17:04,300 --> 00:17:05,530
Full speed ahead!

214
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:01,560
What great swordsmanship!

215
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:13,960
I am Fan Yunxiao.

216
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,690
Are you from the Yuyuan clan?

217
00:18:16,230 --> 00:18:18,380
I'm Qin Mu. I'm from the Imperial Academy.

